com.thinkaurelius.titan.diskstorage.keycolumnvalue

Class SliceQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thinkaurelius.titan.diskstorage.keycolumnvalue.SliceQuery
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FittedSliceQuery, KeyRangeQuery, KeySliceQuery

    public class SliceQuery
extends Object
    Queries for a slice of data identified by a start point (inclusive) and end point (exclusive). Returns all ByteBuffers that lie in this range up to the given limit. If a SliceQuery is marked static it is expected that the result set does not change. (c) Matthias Broecheler (me@matthiasb.com)
